import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { useParams } from 'react-router' import { Detail } from './Detail'; import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux'; import { Add } from '../Action/action'; export default function ProductDetail() { const dispatch=useDispatch(); const send=(element)=>{ dispatch(Add(element)); } const[data,setdata]=useState([]); const {id}=useParams(); const compare = () => { let comparedata = Detail.filter((e) => { return parseInt(e.id) == id; }); setdata(comparedata); }; useEffect(() => { compare(); }, [id]); return (
{data.map((element) => (

{element.title}

4 Reviews

{element.des}

Color
Size
Rs:{element.price}
))}
) }
